Package: cvir
Title: Content Validity Index (CVI) Calculation and Visualization
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Manus", "AI", ,
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "manus.ai@example.com")
Description: Provides functions to calculate various Content Validity Index (CVI) metrics, including Item-level CVI (I-CVI), Scale-level CVI (S-CVI/Ave, S-CVI/UA), and Modified Kappa. It also includes ggplot2-based visualization tools for exploring expert ratings and CVI scores.
